OL,3,CHMRC U-turns on plan to close self-
OL,4,Cassessment phone line after public
OL,5,Coutcry
OL,7,FHM Revenue & Customs' has reversed
OL,8,Fplans to close self-assessment
OL,9,Fhelpline services for six months a
OL,10,Fyear after public outcry.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, had announced that from
OL,13,Fthis year its self-assessment would be
OL,14,Fshut from between April and September,
OL,15,Fwith customers directed to self-serve
OL,16,Fthrough its online services.
OL,18,FHowever, by Wednesday morning, the
OL,19,Frevenue body said it was halting the
OL,20,Fplans in response to feedback.
