OL,7,FHMCR said it will now consider how to
OL,8,Fensure all taxpayers' needs are met
OL,9,Fwhile it continued to shift more
OL,10,Fpeople to online self-service in the
OL,11,Flonger term.
OL,13,FHMRC chief executive Jim Harra:
OL,14,F"Making best use of online services
OL,15,Fallows HMRC to help more taxpayers and
OL,16,Fget the most out of every pound of
OL,17,Ftaxpayers' money by boosting
OL,18,Fproductivity.
