OL,5,Coutcry
OL,7,FShortly before the u-turn from HMRC,
OL,8,FThe Telegraph reported that Chancellor
OL,9,FJeremy Hunt had ordered the tax office
OL,10,Fto scrap the plans.
OL,12,FMPs debated the decision by HMRC and
OL,13,Fthe government's role in it on
OL,14,FWednesday.
OL,16,FShadow Financial Secretary to the
OL,17,FTreasury James Murray said "this is a
OL,18,Fu-turn of quite extraordinary speed
OL,19,Fand indignity.
