OL,3,CHMRC U-turns on plan to close self-
OL,4,Cassessment phone line after public
OL,5,Coutcry
OL,7,F"It is clear the announced closure of
OL,8,Fthe helpline yesterday came not as
OL,9,Fpart of a comprehensive, orderly or
OL,10,Feffective plan to help customers move
OL,11,Fonline, but rather as a panicked
OL,12,Fresponse to HMRC's service levels
OL,13,Fcollapsing to an all-time low.
OL,15,F"It is clear this government is
OL,16,Ffundamentally unstable and has given
OL,17,Fup on serious governing", he said.
