OL,3,CHMRC U-turns on plan to close self-
OL,4,Cassessment phone line after public
OL,5,Coutcry
OL,7,FMP Caroline Nokes said she spoke to
OL,8,Felderly people who were "horrified" at
OL,9,Fthe HMRC announcement on Tuesday,
OL,10,Fasking for reassurance that
OL,11,F"vulnerable people" will still be able
OL,12,Fto use telephone services.
OL,14,FChairwoman of the Treasury Select
OL,15,FCommittee, Harriett Baldwin, said on
OL,16,FTuesday that the move to online
OL,17,Fservices should not be "forced on
OL,18,Ftaxpayers".
