OL,7,FShe said the revenue body has not yet
OL,8,Fdemonstrated that the department or
OL,9,Fthe public "are ready to make such a
OL,10,Fmonumental change to how they resolve
OL,11,Ftax issues".
OL,13,FThe Chartered Institute of Taxation
OL,14,F(CIOT) previously described the plans
OL,15,Fas "misguided".
OL,17,FTina McKenzie, policy chairwoman at
OL,18,Fthe Federation of Small Businesses
OL,19,F(FSB), said on Tuesday that the plans
OL,20,Fwould "be greeted with dismay by
OL,21,Fthousands of small businesses".
